    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>劈腿！？真的要劈腿吗？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>虽然真的对“他”很心动，但是出轨这种事！绝对不行吧？！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >二编：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为没找到可以下架的地方，所以先这样放着</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于中日关系会整体进行大改，剧情会从日本搬到中国</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果后面关系缓和会把日本背景的demo发出，但是正章内容会完全改动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >，，很崩溃啊怎么连ui logo都要改啊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >相关信息</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前会在小红书我个人账号上贴一点工事中内容，ID：睡觉</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Backgrounds:</strong> <br>Unsplash photographers: Nguyễn Hiệp, Luis Gherasim, JAWZ, Jacob Hodgson, Carlos Coronado, Alan Alves, Piya Kirdpanya, Max, Techivation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Icons:</strong> <br>Flaticon creators: th studio, Pixel perfect, Freepik</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D Models:</strong> <br>Fab artist: Rafael Rodrigues</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背景音乐以及cv有点多....等完善之后再统一进行统计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >便于方便整理目前资产所以有些是购入的也归类进来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真的非常感谢大家的分享....省了好多好多钱TT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
